"Use of the thing
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" I think I want to apply
"set hidden on
"set bufhidden hide
"which I think will mean that I can change between buffers without saving
"the changes and not lose what I've done

"Automatically save and load folds
"I think also saves last position I was in
au BufWinLeave ?* mkview
au BufWinEnter ?* silent loadview

"Make it so I can switch between buffers without having to save
set hidden

"Show commands as I'm typing
set showcmd

"Make no automatic backup files
set nobackup

"This gets rid of the foldcolumn that is a remnant of vimdiff
"au BufWinEnter ?* set foldcolumn=0


